        <name>block_start</name>
        <qualifiedname>bt_mesh_blob_io::block_start</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Block start callback. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Called when a new block is opened for sending. Each block is only sent once, and are always sent in increasing order. The data chunks inside a single block may be requested out of order and multiple times.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>io</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>BLOB stream. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>xfer</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>BLOB transfer. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>block</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Block that was started. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
